00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,360
I'd better ask Chief Xing in person.

287
00:15:26,559 --> 00:15:27,240
Hello?

288
00:15:28,279 --> 00:15:29,039
Mingliang.

289
00:15:30,879 --> 00:15:31,639
Where are you?

290
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,639
Okay, I'll wait for you.

291
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:51,919
Chief Xing.

292
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:54,879
What are you doing here?

293
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:58,840
I have to face it sooner or later.

294
00:16:00,399 --> 00:16:01,399
Has Li Kaiyang confessed?

295
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:02,919
That mouth of his...

296
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,080
He's a tough nut to crack.

297
00:16:04,639 --> 00:16:05,879
Unless you handle it yourself.

298
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,759
The livestream location,

299
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:11,879
have you locked it down?

300
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,000
So you already know.

301
00:16:16,159 --> 00:16:17,240
It's all my fault.

302
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:20,200
I failed in my duties as a father.

303
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,600
All the consequences,

304
00:16:25,159 --> 00:16:26,159
I'll bear them myself.

305
00:16:27,399 --> 00:16:27,960
Yonglin.

306
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:29,279
Mingliang.

307
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,159
He just called and said

308
00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:32,279
he's currently

309
00:16:32,480 --> 00:16:33,559
On the way to surrender.

310
00:16:34,559 --> 00:16:35,200
Really?

311
00:16:35,679 --> 00:16:36,879
Absolutely certain.

312
00:16:37,159 --> 00:16:38,279
That animal.

313
00:16:50,440 --> 00:16:51,080
Mingliang.

314
00:16:51,559 --> 00:16:53,279
Did you take Zhao Ruolan?

315
00:16:53,879 --> 00:16:54,399
Yes.

316
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,440
Where is she now?

317
00:16:56,159 --> 00:16:56,679
Tell me.

318
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,159
Where is she now?

319
00:16:59,399 --> 00:17:00,639
In what capacity are you asking me?

320
00:17:01,639 --> 00:17:02,799
As your father.

321
00:17:03,279 --> 00:17:03,759
Speak.

322
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,880
Where did you take Zhao Ruolan?

323
00:17:07,559 --> 00:17:08,680
She's my girlfriend.

324
00:17:09,039 --> 00:17:10,000
What business is it of yours?

325
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,359
You animal!

326
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:14,599
Captain Wang.

327
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:18,200
Is this how you treat someone who came to surrender?

328
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:22,000
Interrogate him now.

329
00:17:22,519 --> 00:17:23,279
Interrogate him thoroughly.

330
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:25,039
Make him confess everything clearly.

331
00:17:42,799 --> 00:17:45,240
You came to surrender, yet you say nothing.

332
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,480
What are you really getting at?

333
00:17:47,319 --> 00:17:48,000
Captain Wang.

334
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,960
Do you really think I'm guilty?

335
00:17:51,720 --> 00:17:52,640
You're not guilty?

336
00:17:53,960 --> 00:17:55,920
Wasn't it you who kidnapped Zhao Ruolan?

337
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:57,680
Kidnapped?

338
00:17:58,640 --> 00:17:59,839
How could I possibly kidnap her?
